h1. Description

    Open source implementation of the Modbus TCP / IP protocol in server mode. The server allows consultation of the ModbusDevice devices created in memory.
    It implements the following functions:
        * Read coils
        * Write single coil
        * Write multiple coils
        * Read input register
        * Read holding registes
        * Write single register
        * Write multiple registers
        * Read/Write multiple registers
        * Mask write register
        * Read FIFO queue


